So don't ever interfere with my daughter and me anymore.

792
00:52:57,990 --> 00:53:01,840
If you're tired, please go home and take a break, Madam.

793
00:53:01,840 --> 00:53:04,810
It must be a happy ending.

794
00:53:04,810 --> 00:53:10,010
For me, Cheol Woong, and my husband, too.

795
00:53:12,770 --> 00:53:16,000
It will be.

796
00:53:16,000 --> 00:53:17,550
NSA Director's Special Aide?

797
00:53:17,550 --> 00:53:20,670
I've been assigned a critical secret order by the president.

798
00:53:20,670 --> 00:53:22,920
I need someone I can trust entirely.

799
00:53:22,920 --> 00:53:24,610
That's why  I called you.

800
00:53:24,610 --> 00:53:29,070
But... I like my job as a prosecutor.

801
00:53:29,070 --> 00:53:30,900
If you want to go back to

802
00:53:30,900 --> 00:53:34,200
the prosecution, when this job is done, I won't stop you.

803
00:53:35,310 --> 00:53:38,070
Just think you're helping me.

804
00:53:38,070 --> 00:53:40,690
What's the important secret order?

805
00:53:40,690 --> 00:53:42,670
Northern policy.

806
00:53:42,670 --> 00:53:45,890
"Northern policy"?

807
00:53:45,890 --> 00:53:50,110

808
00:54:03,500 --> 00:54:07,490

