00:56:05,640 --> 00:56:07,540
Give me back all my money.

814
00:56:07,540 --> 00:56:10,900
I know you guys run a gambling scam.

815
00:56:10,900 --> 00:56:14,460
Give back all my money before I kill you!

816
00:56:14,460 --> 00:56:16,020
How much?

817
00:56:16,020 --> 00:56:17,970
Ten million yen ($182,000 in 1989).

818
00:56:20,670 --> 00:56:22,340
There.

819
00:56:22,990 --> 00:56:24,950
You can have that.

820
00:56:25,980 --> 00:56:28,400
Doo Hak, fighting!

821
00:56:29,890 --> 00:56:36,400
♫  Will I be able to come to you again?  ♫

822
00:56:36,400 --> 00:56:43,090
♫  Trembling eyes, they're even more sorrowful  ♫

823
00:56:43,090 --> 00:56:49,960
♫  Above the rough sky, my heart floats away  ♫

824
00:56:49,960 --> 00:56:56,940
♫  Only your name is engraved like this  ♫

825
00:57:33,150 --> 00:57:35,390
- All good? 
 - Yes, to the dot.

826
00:57:35,390 --> 00:57:40,260
We'll be having important guests here tomorrow. Make sure to prepare properly.

827
00:57:40,260 --> 00:57:42,100
When are we going to Korea?

828
00:57:42,100 --> 00:57:44,760
I choose the time.

829
00:57:44,760 --> 00:57:46,810
You'd better keep your promise.

830
00:57:46,810 --> 00:57:49,520
I also choose whether or not to keep promises.

831
00:57:49,520 --> 00:57:52,390
Only those with power get to doubt and object.

832
00:57:52,390 --> 00:57:56,390
Before you can do that, hide your true feelings.

833
00:57:56,390 --> 00:57:59,920
That's how you'll be able to survive.

