00:58:01,680 --> 00:58:03,530
 What's that?

835
00:58:04,300 --> 00:58:05,900
 It looks like a person.

836
00:58:05,900 --> 00:58:08,520
 Hey. Pull him up.

837
00:58:08,520 --> 00:58:10,750
 Pull him up! Hurry!

838
00:58:10,750 --> 00:58:12,690
 Returning from visiting the home country after a long time,

