00:58:18,070 --> 00:58:20,740
 - He's alive! 
 - Hey, his wound is deep!

842
00:58:20,740 --> 00:58:23,180
 Hurry! Move quickly!

843
00:58:23,180 --> 00:58:25,160
You lost your life once.

844
00:58:25,160 --> 00:58:28,860
Shouldn't you try to stay alive for a long time now?

845
00:58:48,280 --> 00:58:51,260
Thank you so much for coming this far.

846
00:58:51,260 --> 00:58:52,810
My name is Chae Dong Pal.

847
00:58:52,810 --> 00:58:55,400
Nice to meet you. I'm Hwang Choong Sung.

848
00:58:55,400 --> 00:59:00,330
And this is Prosecutor Choi Cheol Woong, my aide.

849
00:59:01,530 --> 00:59:04,260
I brought some good rice wine from Korea.

