00:59:20,630 --> 00:59:23,880
And North Korea also interferes with some success.

856
00:59:23,880 --> 00:59:27,620
I know you have been making deals in Kazakhstan for a long time.

857
00:59:27,620 --> 00:59:29,070
If you help us...

858
00:59:29,070 --> 00:59:32,470
The South Korean government will compensate you for sure.

859
00:59:32,470 --> 00:59:34,880
Sounds great.

860
00:59:34,880 --> 00:59:37,690
I'll also do my best then.

861
00:59:37,690 --> 00:59:39,840
Thank you!

862
00:59:42,210 --> 00:59:47,140
My granddaughter will be going to Korea first, as my representative.

863
00:59:47,140 --> 00:59:49,840
Oh, there she comes, just in time.

864
00:59:49,840 --> 00:59:53,720
All right. This is my granddaughter, Chae Ha Yeon.

